data.description: Sprawling Well Maintained Brick/Vinyl 3-Bedroom Ranch w/2-Car Attached Garage on a Large Level (0.6 Acres) Yard.  Located on a Private Cul-De-Sac. Oak Eat-In Kitchen w/Ceramic Floors. Huge (27x20) Family Room w/Brick Gas Fireplace, Vaulted Ceilings w/Skylight, Laminate Flooring and Anderson Glass Sliders Leading to Private Covered (28x14) Patio.  Over 1800 SqFt of Living Space. Formal Dining Room off EIK w/Laminate Flooring. Solid 6-Panel Interior Doors Throughout 1st Floor.  Neutral Decor.  Full Basement w/Exercise Room/Office/4th Bedroom, Full Bath and Walkout to Backyard. Solar Panels Installed on Roof 2021 Providing FREE Electricity.  Large Back Yard w/Garden Shed. Minutes to Beaver Valley Mall, I-376, Penn State Beaver Campus, Shell Cracker Plant. Zoned Residential/Commercial.
